<div id="grad1"><h1><span style="color:var(--ds-text-inverse,#ffffff);">Threat-focused Defense</span></h1></div>

<ac:structured-macro ac:name="panel">
  <ac:parameter ac:name="borderColor">#1c5e98</ac:parameter>
  <ac:parameter ac:name="borderWidth">2</ac:parameter>
  <ac:parameter ac:name="title">Welcome!</ac:parameter>
  <ac:parameter ac:name="titleBGColor">#1c5e98</ac:parameter>
  <ac:parameter ac:name="titleColor">#FFFFFF</ac:parameter>
  <ac:rich-text-body>
    <p><strong>Security Vision</strong></p>
    <p>Welcome to the central hub for the Threat Focused Controls/Defense Program. All metrics and insights are automated and updated in real time to ensure total accuracy. Our mission is to reduce known exposure <span style="color:var(--ds-text,#172b4d);">to specific security threats (e.g., Insider risk, physical access to our hardware/data centers, etc) affecting Cloudflare.</span></p>
  </ac:rich-text-body>
</ac:structured-macro>
<p>
